# URL of the @vobo/server Socket.IO server.
#
# Leave this UNSET for local + LAN play: the client auto-connects to the same
# host that served the page, on port 3001 (open http://<your-LAN-IP>:3000 on
# another device and it will reach http://<your-LAN-IP>:3001 automatically).
#
# Set it only to point at a fixed/remote server (e.g. production):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SERVER_URL=https://api.example.com
